{
  "info": {
    "name": "NodeProject - Departments",
    "description": "Department endpoints. Run folders in numeric order (1-6): Create Department first (auto-saves {{departmentId}}), then the rest reuse that id automatically, ending with Delete. Requires {{token}} (get it from the Users collection's Login request) and {{employeeId}} (from Users Register/Login) for step 5. All routes require a Bearer token; Create/Update/Delete require an Admin role token.",
